---
// Disclaimer page — proof-of-concept port of /disclaimer.html.
//
// What changed vs. the legacy HTML:
//   - All <head> meta, OG, schema, GA, fonts, CSS → moved into <BaseLayout>.
//   - Nav and Footer → <Nav /> and <Footer /> components, no more
//     copy-pasting the same 40 lines.
//   - Legal-doc styles moved into a single global <style is:global> block
//     at the top of the page (was a <style> tag in <head>).
//   - Internal links updated from .html to clean URLs (/contact, /privacy-policy, …).
//   - Canonical URL updated to the clean form (was /disclaimer.html).
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@graph': [
    {
      '@type': 'BreadcrumbList',
      itemListElement: [
        { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 1, name: 'Home', item: 'https://projecthome.sg/' },
        { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 2, name: 'Disclaimer', item: 'https://projecthome.sg/disclaimer' },
      ],
    },
    {
      '@type': 'WebPage',
      '@id': 'https://projecthome.sg/disclaimer#webpage',
      url: 'https://projecthome.sg/disclaimer',
      name: 'Disclaimer — ProjectHome.sg',
      inLanguage: 'en-SG',
      isPartOf: { '@id': 'https://projecthome.sg/#website' },
    },
  ],
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer | ProjectHome.sg"
  description="Information on ProjectHome.sg (PHsg) is for general guidance only. Read our disclaimer on accuracy, liability, investment risk and the importance of independent due diligence."
  keywords="ProjectHome.sg disclaimer, PHsg disclaimer, Singapore property disclaimer, investment risk, due diligence"
  canonical="https://projecthome.sg/disclaimer"
  ogTitle="Disclaimer | ProjectHome.sg"
  ogDescription="ProjectHome.sg content is general guidance only. Review our disclaimer before acting on any information."
  twitterDescription="ProjectHome.sg content is general guidance only. Review our disclaimer before acting on any information."
  schema={schema}
>

  <style is:global slot="head-extra">
    .legal-doc h2 { color: var(--copper); font-family: var(--font-sans); letter-spacing: 0.04em; font-size: 1.25rem; }
    .legal-doc h2:first-of-type { margin-top: 0; }
    .legal-doc p, .legal-doc li { color: rgba(247, 241, 232, 0.92); }
    .legal-doc a { color: var(--copper); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
    .legal-doc a:hover { color: #f0bb84; }
    .legal-doc strong { color: var(--cream); }
    .legal-doc ul { padding-left: 1.25rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem; }
    .legal-doc li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  </style>

  <section class="page-banner">
    <div class="page-banner-inner">
      <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <span class="current" aria-current="page">Disclaimer</span>
      </nav>
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
      <p>Everything published on ProjectHome.sg (&ldquo;PHsg&rdquo;) is general information, not personalised advice. Please read this disclaimer before relying on anything you find here.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="guides" style="background: var(--teal);">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="legal-doc" style="max-width:820px; margin:0 auto; color:rgba(247,241,232,0.92); line-height:1.75;">

        <p style="font-size:0.92rem; color:rgba(247,241,232,0.65);"><strong>Last updated:</strong> 31 May 2026</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:36px;">1. For information only</h2>
        <p>ProjectHome.sg publishes property guides, market commentary, new launch reviews and related content for general information purposes only. The site is intended to help readers think more clearly about Singapore property decisions &mdash; it is not, and should not be treated as, a personal recommendation to buy, sell, lease or finance any specific property, project or unit.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:36px;">2. No warranty as to accuracy or completeness</h2>
        <p>We make a genuine effort to keep our content accurate, current and balanced &mdash; drawing on URA, HDB, CEA, JTC and developer data where appropriate. Even so, ProjectHome.sg, its co-founders and contributors give no representations or warranties, whether express or implied, as to the completeness, accuracy, reliability, suitability, timeliness or availability of any information, opinion, image, chart, link, product or service on this website. Property markets move, rules change, and unit-level facts (PSF, layout, view, stack, balance units) must always be verified against the developer&rsquo;s latest sales material or the URA REALIS records at the point of decision.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:36px;">3. Not financial, legal or tax advice</h2>
        <p>Nothing on ProjectHome.sg constitutes financial, investment, legal, tax or mortgage advice, and no fiduciary relationship is created by your use of the site. Before committing to a property transaction you should obtain independent advice from suitably qualified professionals &mdash; mortgage brokers or bankers (for IPA and loan structuring), conveyancing lawyers (for OTP, S&amp;P and ABSD matters), tax advisors (for stamp duties and rental income), and licensed financial advisors (for portfolio impact).</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:36px;">4. Property investment carries risk</h2>
        <p>All investments &mdash; including residential, commercial and overseas real estate &mdash; involve risk. Past performance of a district, project or asset class is not a reliable indicator of future results. Capital values, rental yields and resale liquidity can fall as well as rise, and may be affected by cooling measures, interest rate movements, supply pipelines, en-bloc cycles and macro conditions beyond anyone&rsquo;s control. You should never commit to a purchase you cannot comfortably finance through a downturn.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:36px;">5. Do your own due diligence</h2>
        <p>Readers are strongly encouraged to conduct their own due diligence before acting on anything published here. That means:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Confirming eligibility (HDB, EC, ABSD rates, citizenship rules) with HDB and IRAS directly.</li>
          <li>Cross-checking PSF benchmarks against URA REALIS and developer price lists at the time of decision.</li>
          <li>Reviewing the actual unit, stack, floor plan and view in person &mdash; not relying solely on showflat renderings.</li>
          <li>Stress-testing affordability under MAS&rsquo;s prevailing TDSR and MSR rules.</li>
          <li>Reading the OTP, S&amp;P and developer disclosures carefully with your appointed conveyancing lawyer.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="margin-top:36px;">6. Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, ProjectHome.sg, its co-founders Jason Sim and Renee Lim, Huttons Asia Pte Ltd, and any contributor or service provider, shall not be liable for any loss or damage &mdash; including but not limited to direct, indirect, incidental, consequential or punitive loss, loss of profit, loss of opportunity, or loss of data &mdash; arising out of, or in connection with, your use of, or reliance on, this website or any content, product, service, link or related material contained on it. Your use of the site is at your own risk.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:36px;">7. Third-party links and references</h2>
        <p>The site links to or references external resources such as URA, HDB, CEA, IRAS, MAS, developer microsites, news outlets and YouTube videos for the reader&rsquo;s convenience. We do not control, and are not responsible for, the content, accuracy or availability of those external sites; the inclusion of a link does not imply endorsement.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:36px;">8. Forward-looking statements</h2>
        <p>Articles on ProjectHome.sg may include forward-looking views &mdash; for example, on launch pricing, district outlook or market direction. These are opinions based on currently available information and inherently involve uncertainty. They should not be relied upon as guarantees of future outcomes.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:36px;">9. Advisory relationship is separate</h2>
        <p>ProjectHome.sg is a publishing brand. Jason Sim and Renee Lim are CEA-registered salespersons with Huttons Asia Pte Ltd (Agency Licence No: L3008899K). Should you choose to engage them for personalised advisory or transaction services, that engagement is governed by Huttons Asia&rsquo;s separate terms and the CEA Practice Guidelines &mdash; not by this disclaimer or anything published on this website.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:36px;">10. Changes to this disclaimer</h2>
        <p>We may update this disclaimer from time to time to reflect changes in our content, services or applicable rules. The &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date at the top of this page indicates when it was last revised. Your continued use of the site after an update constitutes acceptance of the revised disclaimer.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top:36px;">11. Get in touch</h2>
        <p>If anything on the site looks inaccurate, out of date or unclear &mdash; or if you would like personalised guidance instead of general information &mdash; please reach out:</p>
        <div style="margin-top:18px; padding:22px; background:rgba(247, 241, 232, 0.06); border:1px solid rgba(209, 149, 87, 0.2); border-radius:var(--radius);">
          <p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;"><strong>ProjectHome.sg</strong></p>
          <p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;">WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/6582822486?text=Hi%2C%20I%27m%20enquiring%20via%20ProjectHome.sg%2C%20regarding%20the%20Disclaimer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">+65 8282 2486</a></p>
          <p style="margin:0;">Email enquiry: <a href="/contact">via the contact form</a></p>
        </div>

      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-strip">
    <h2>Want personalised guidance instead?</h2>
    <p>General information only gets you so far. WhatsApp for a real-person conversation on your specific situation.</p>
    <a href="https://wa.me/6582822486?text=Hi%2C%20I%27m%20enquiring%20via%20ProjectHome.sg%2C%20regarding%20" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-secondary">Open WhatsApp Chat</a>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
